{"tid":2001850,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"突發 - 路透社記者報導香港抗爭 贏普立茲獎","createTime":"2020-05-04T23:58:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T00:33:37.000Z","uid":12929,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d9f1a43e06dc29ee944b88b74d90f64b03d38940","tid":2001850,"uid":12929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T23:58:01.000Z","msg":"路透社攝影師Tyrone Siu，Adnan Abidi，Ammar Awad，Anushree Fadnavis，Willy Kurniawan，Leah Millis，Athit Perawongmetha，Thomas Peter，Kai Pfaffenbach，Jorge Silva和Susan Vera因拍攝去年在香港展開多月的親民主，反政府抗議活動，<span style=\"color: red;\">在&ldquo;突發新聞攝影&rdquo;類別中穫獎</span>。<br />\n<br />\n普立茲策委員會承認路透社的報導&ldquo;是在香港民眾<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">抗議中國政府侵犯其公民自由並捍衛該地區自治</span></strong>的情況下，為香港拍攝的寬廣而具有啟發性的照片。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s4.reutersmedia.net/resources/r/?m=02&amp;d=20200504&amp;t=2&amp;i=1517444381&amp;w=780&amp;fh=&amp;fw=&amp;ll=&amp;pl=&amp;sq=&amp;r=2020-05-04T195403Z_35426_MRPRC2VHG9EXRJ6_RTRMADP_0_USA-PULITZER\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs4.reutersmedia.net%2Fresources%2Fr%2F%3Fm%3D02%26d%3D20200504%26t%3D2%26i%3D1517444381%26w%3D780%26fh%3D%26fw%3D%26ll%3D%26pl%3D%26sq%3D%26r%3D2020-05-04T195403Z_35426_MRPRC2VHG9EXRJ6_RTRMADP_0_USA-PULITZER&h=e6737cbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s4.reutersmedia.net/resources/r/?m=02&amp;d=20200504&amp;t=2&amp;i=1517444386&amp;w=780&amp;fh=&amp;fw=&amp;ll=&amp;pl=&amp;sq=&amp;r=2020-05-04T195403Z_35426_MRPRC2VHG9IL6A6_RTRMADP_0_USA-PULITZER\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs4.reutersmedia.net%2Fresources%2Fr%2F%3Fm%3D02%26d%3D20200504%26t%3D2%26i%3D1517444386%26w%3D780%26fh%3D%26fw%3D%26ll%3D%26pl%3D%26sq%3D%26r%3D2020-05-04T195403Z_35426_MRPRC2VHG9IL6A6_RTRMADP_0_USA-PULITZER&h=a3702d5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s4.reutersmedia.net/resources/r/?m=02&amp;d=20200504&amp;t=2&amp;i=1517444394&amp;w=780&amp;fh=&amp;fw=&amp;ll=&amp;pl=&amp;sq=&amp;r=2020-05-04T195403Z_